Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.application

Class Main

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.application.Main
  • public class Main
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles the main loop where the game runs. It also sends all the info needed to different classes every tick.
